overview: These horned up muscle men take no prisoners as they strong-arm their way through a new cast of fist-hungry hunks in Strong-Armed 2. This raunchy continuation of the Strong-Armed Trilogy from the Club Inferno Hot Hand Collection features five scenes of elbow-swallowing, pud-pounding, ass-licking action. Now bend over and take it like a man!
title: Strong-Armed 2
